These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, domino
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, marigold
House: wooden, cape-cod, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian, australian
1. the person who growsdahlia is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the australian is on the far left##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the pakistani##1
4. the wooden house is the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
6. the person playing domino is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the futuristic house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Game      | domino  | monopoly       | mah-jongg   |
| Flower          | marigold | balloon-flower | dahlia |
| House         | wooden  | futuristic | cape-cod    |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani       | brazilian      |

