.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, go
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, art-deco
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, baseball, ice-hockey
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, chef, librarian
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the chef##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the librarian is on the far left##1
6. the librarian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Game          | chess      | bridge  | go        |
| House         | art-deco | craftsman | gothic-revival |
| Sport   | lacrosse | baseball | ice-hockey       |
| Job           | librarian     | chef     | accountant      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, cranberry
City: nizza, london, marseilles
3 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, davidoff
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Food      | grapefruit    | nectarine        | cranberry |
| City           | london    | marseilles | nizza    |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon             | monopoly  |
| Cigar     | davidoff     | alhambra                | prince  |

