.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, go
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, swisher
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, weightlifting, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Game          | domino    | go  | scrabble      |
| Beverage           | soy-milk    | lemonade | iced-tea |
| Cigar   | swisher   | alhambra  | blend     |
| Sport   | soccer | weightlifting    | swimming      |

