.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, poker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, tulip
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, turkish, italian
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, orange, azure
1. the brazilian is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person who growstulip is the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes coral is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the italian is the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | poker | monopoly     | backgammon   |
| Flower           | tulip       | dahlia   | aconite     |
| Nationality   | turkish     | brazilian | italian |
| Color           | azure      | coral         | orange  |

