.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, american, indonesian
House: ranch-style, cottage, farmhouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, weightlifting
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, ferret
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the american##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Nationality          | indonesian       | american         | chinese   |
| House           | ranch-style | farmhouse | cottage |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | parkour        | weightlifting        |
| Pet   | rabbit      | mouse           | ferret        |

