.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, davidoff, swisher
City: rome, venice, boston
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, black, fuchsia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Cigar         | davidoff   | swisher | montecristo |
| City   | rome | boston         | venice       |
| Color           | yellow      | fuchsia      | black         |
| Sport     | water-polo      | biathlon         | rowing          |

