.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
City: new-york, colone, boston
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, turkish, polish
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, canasta
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to colone is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the brazilian is the person playing canasta##1
5. the polish is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| City       | colone            | new-york      | boston  |
| Nationality         | polish | brazilian | turkish |
| Game         | poker               | canasta | billiard |
| Birthday   | may             | july       | march      |

