3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
