.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, poker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, june
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, oliveros, fonseca
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, weightlifting
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Game           | go | poker | monopoly |
| Birthday   | june        | february       | july     |
| Cigar   | oliveros     | fonseca         | bolivar     |
| Sport     | weightlifting | surfing          | volleyball      |

