.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, australian, chinese
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, boat, subway
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, lavender, chestnut
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, fisherman
1. the fisherman is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
3. the italian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the firefighter is on the left of the australian##1
5. the fisherman is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Nationality      | chinese    | australian | italian |
| Transport   | boat | bike     | subway     |
| Color   | chestnut        | lavender        | ebony        |
| Job           | firefighter    | fisherman         | designer     |

