.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-15::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, cat, goat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, documentary
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, victorian
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, yellow, brown
1. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person who likes yellow is the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Pet      | goat | pony | cat       |
| Movie-Genre          | documentary     | comedy   | superhero       |
| House         | craftsman  | victorian   | gothic-revival |
| Color   | yellow   | brown       | coral  |

