.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, gardening
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, september
City: nizza, miami, paris
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the dutch is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby      | gardening      | chess    | skydiving    |
| Nationality          | dutch         | british    | australian   |
| Birthday           | february | september | august |
| City   | paris         | nizza     | miami    |

