3. the ranch-style house is the person playing billiard##1
4. the chaman-smoker is the cape-cod house##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing whist is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| House      | cape-cod         | ranch-style     | colonial     |
| Nationality           | japanese        | ranch-stylecher | thai |
| Cigar   | chaman        | bolivar   | bluemaster    |
