.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, librarian, journalist
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, coffee
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, game, vegafina
City: san-francisco, london, hannover
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Job          | journalist     | librarian    | software-developer    |
| Beverage         | mirinda | coffee | sprite     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | game      | vegafina        |
| City         | san-francisco   | london   | hannover |

 